        public IdeAddressSpec.Builder setPrimary(java.lang.Boolean primary)
        Flag specifying whether the device should be attached to the primary or secondary IDE adapter of the virtual machine. If null, the server will choose a adapter with an available connection. If no IDE connections are available, the request will be rejected.
